				<STRONG>I do know what happened.</STRONG>&nbsp;  I forget that, when I paste in HTML from another page that has line breaks in its markup, those will be turned into &lt;br /&gt; elements by Blogger.&nbsp; I asked for that problem.&nbsp; The problem I didn't ask for was the fact that line breaks <EM>inside of a tag</EM> (i.e., between attributes) lead to the same mindless behavior.&nbsp; This leads me to an interesting rant about executable specifications that will come out soon, somewhere.<br />
